1. *Vezi* se na njegovu prošlost. (He connects to his past.)
2. Ona je uspostavila vezu sa njom. (She established a connection with her.)
3. Oni su se pronašli kroz vezu. (They found each other through connection.)
4. On je napravio vezu sa njom. (He made a connection with her.)
5. Ona je pokušala da održi vezu. (She tried to maintain the connection.)
6. Njihovo povezivanje je bilo uspješno. (Their connection was successful.)
7. Oni su imali veoma jaku vezu. (They had a very strong connection.)
8. Njegova veza sa njom je bila očigledna. (His connection with her was obvious.)
9. Oni su imali veoma blisku vezu. (They had a very close connection.)
10. Ona je napravila vezu sa njim. (She made a connection with him.)